description.value: Palooka Token (PLK) is the ultimate meme token, inspired by the lovable and clumsy character Palooka. As a thin, goofy, and slightly ineffectual crypto figure, Palooka brings humor and fun to the crypto space. PLK is community-driven, with regular memes, contests, and events to keep engagement high. Join the Palooka revolution and ride the wave to the moon!
